In [13]:
def ceiling_correction(num):
    ceiling_height = float(num)
    if ceiling_height >= 20:
        return ceiling_height/10
    return ceiling_height
In [14]:
data['ceiling_height'] = data['ceiling_height'].apply(ceiling_correction)

In [16]:
def locality_name_corr(name):
    split_name = name.split(' ')
    del_list = ['', '', '', '', '', '', '', '']
    result = [i for i in split_name if i not in del_list]
    return ' '.join(result)
In [17]:
data['locality_name'] = data['locality_name'].apply(locality_name_corr)   #

def floor_type(num1, num2):     
    
    if num1 == 1:
        return ''
    if num1 == num2:
        return ''
    return ''

def upper_bound(column):
    Q1 = data[column].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = data[column].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
    return upper
